WEBVTT

00:01:40.520 --> 00:01:45.930
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:49.020
[Episode 10]

00:02:06.710 --> 00:02:07.600
Sorry.

00:02:07.630 --> 00:02:09.880
I got your dad a little too drunk,
so he fell asleep.

00:02:09.880 --> 00:02:12.740
It's fine. He can fall asleep
after a single capful.

00:02:16.870 --> 00:02:18.240
But think about

00:02:18.430 --> 00:02:19.690
what I just said again.

00:02:21.150 --> 00:02:23.680
My mom was a Model Worker
of the city back then.

00:02:23.710 --> 00:02:24.760
Just like you.

00:02:25.650 --> 00:02:26.710
She had to do her job well,

00:02:26.710 --> 00:02:28.420
and take care of me and my brother.

00:02:28.420 --> 00:02:29.680
It was too exhausting.

00:02:30.550 --> 00:02:32.110
Anti-drug work is hard.

00:02:32.130 --> 00:02:34.150
There's no need to push yourself so hard,

00:02:34.150 --> 00:02:35.360
trying to be a good mother

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.840
and a good cop at the same time.

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:39.329
Haizhou isn't Beijing or Shanghai.

00:02:39.390 --> 00:02:41.840
City No. 3 High School isn't much better
than Nuanfeng County High School, is it?

00:02:41.840 --> 00:02:43.390
Is it really worth coming
to the Narcotics Unit

00:02:43.390 --> 00:02:44.550
just for your kids?

00:02:47.910 --> 00:02:49.280
For the sake of us fighting side by side

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:50.800
all this time,

00:02:51.220 --> 00:02:52.840
and for the sake of your sincere attempt

00:02:52.840 --> 00:02:55.030
to persuade me just now,

00:02:55.030 --> 00:02:56.870
I'm going to tell you a secret.

00:02:58.030 --> 00:02:59.680
I haven't told anyone about this.

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:01.080
Don't you dare spread it.

00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:02.080
Go ahead.

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:04.840
I actually don't care

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:06.900
where my two kids go to middle school.

00:03:08.070 --> 00:03:09.830
That's just my excuse.

00:03:10.150 --> 00:03:12.030
Consider it a shield.

00:03:18.030 --> 00:03:19.680
When I applied to the police academy,

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:21.010
there were two reasons.

00:03:22.030 --> 00:03:24.690
First, I wanted to protect
the people around me.

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:25.960
Second,

00:03:27.150 --> 00:03:28.990
I think being a cop is exciting.

00:03:29.030 --> 00:03:30.090
I like excitement.

00:03:31.430 --> 00:03:33.150
And I'm quite competitive.

00:03:33.990 --> 00:03:35.190
I want to earn merits.

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:37.079
I keep thinking how great it would be

00:03:37.079 --> 00:03:38.610
to crack a big case someday.

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:39.840
But tell me,

00:03:40.590 --> 00:03:41.910
in a county town like this,

00:03:41.910 --> 00:03:43.510
where would I find a big case?

00:03:43.590 --> 00:03:44.310
It's nothing more than

00:03:44.310 --> 00:03:46.150
finding lost bicycles

00:03:46.150 --> 00:03:48.350
or returning lost cats to their owners.

00:03:48.829 --> 00:03:49.690
But my life goal

00:03:49.910 --> 00:03:52.190
has never actually been realized.

00:03:52.760 --> 00:03:53.670
I feel like

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:55.960
I can do this job well,

00:03:55.960 --> 00:03:57.220
and I want to do it well.

00:03:57.430 --> 00:03:58.590
I just need

00:03:58.960 --> 00:04:00.080
a bigger platform.

00:04:01.310 --> 00:04:03.080
That's why I want
to go to the City Bureau.

00:04:03.080 --> 00:04:04.480
I've always wanted to go.

00:04:05.870 --> 00:04:07.990
Then why use that as a shield?

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:10.560
Every cop wants to advance

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:11.690
and crack big cases.

00:04:12.800 --> 00:04:13.470
It's not shameful.

00:04:13.470 --> 00:04:14.750
Why couldn't you just say it?

00:04:14.750 --> 00:04:17.279
You're a man.
Of course you don't understand.

00:04:17.870 --> 00:04:20.180
It's not easy for a woman
to build a career,

00:04:20.180 --> 00:04:21.740
especially as a cop.

00:04:22.390 --> 00:04:24.550
Leaving early
and returning late every day...

00:04:24.550 --> 00:04:25.810
I think it's hard work.

00:04:25.890 --> 00:04:27.490
But even if you work this way,

00:04:28.360 --> 00:04:30.310
there'll still be plenty of idiots around

00:04:30.310 --> 00:04:31.950
gossiping and judging you.

00:04:31.970 --> 00:04:32.630
They say,

00:04:32.630 --> 00:04:34.360
"Look at her, neglecting her family

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:35.690
and ignoring her kids."

00:04:36.190 --> 00:04:38.120
They say all kinds of nasty things.

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:40.000
If I didn't have this shield,

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:41.860
if I hadn't come up with this trick,

00:04:41.860 --> 00:04:44.840
do you think my transfer application
would reach the city?

00:04:44.840 --> 00:04:46.180
It would've been blocked
in the county long ago.

00:04:46.180 --> 00:04:48.680
I bet Director Dai
would have suppressed it himself.

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:49.480
Now it's fine.

00:04:50.070 --> 00:04:51.870
Everything is going as I wished.

00:04:52.190 --> 00:04:54.520
I've been transferred to the City Bureau.

00:04:54.760 --> 00:04:56.880
We're cracking big cases now.

00:04:56.909 --> 00:04:59.640
My two kids can go to school downtown.

00:05:00.630 --> 00:05:02.040
It feels perfect.

00:05:02.510 --> 00:05:03.510
A total bullseye.

00:05:04.480 --> 00:05:05.190
I get it.

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:06.750
I get it.

00:05:06.830 --> 00:05:07.950
I understand,

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:10.030
but I feel like

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:12.240
something has been turned upside down.

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:13.310
Nothing's been turned upside down.

00:05:13.310 --> 00:05:14.240
You're just tired.

00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:15.430
Your ride isn't here yet?

00:05:15.430 --> 00:05:15.870
It's here.

00:05:15.870 --> 00:05:16.700
It's been waiting down there for a while.

00:05:16.700 --> 00:05:17.480
Why didn't you say so?

00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:18.800
I walked all this way with you.

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.240
I thought you wanted to walk me out.

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:21.120
You're so full of yourself.

00:05:21.120 --> 00:05:23.210
You're being discharged tomorrow, right?

00:05:23.210 --> 00:05:25.620
I happen to be processing
my transfer tomorrow.

00:05:25.620 --> 00:05:26.240
I heard

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:28.360
you're moving after you get out?

00:05:28.950 --> 00:05:30.270
I plan to move to Yuelai.

00:05:30.270 --> 00:05:32.470
See if I can catch Lv Deli's accomplice.

00:05:33.130 --> 00:05:34.180
I can go there too.

00:05:34.500 --> 00:05:36.720
Working from home isn't very convenient.

00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:37.590
Then let's meet there

00:05:37.590 --> 00:05:38.310
the day after tomorrow.

00:05:38.310 --> 00:05:39.300
I'll go over then.

00:05:39.300 --> 00:05:39.830
Go ahead.

00:05:42.060 --> 00:05:42.450
Okay.

00:05:43.210 --> 00:05:45.159
With your leg like that,
stop running around for no reason.

00:05:45.159 --> 00:05:46.000
Okay, I know.

00:05:46.190 --> 00:05:46.560
Bye.

00:05:46.630 --> 00:05:47.240
I'm heading back.

00:05:47.240 --> 00:05:47.600
Bye.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:47.920
Bye.

00:05:49.630 --> 00:05:50.750
I walked all this way out,

00:05:50.750 --> 00:05:52.150
now I have to walk back alone.

00:05:52.150 --> 00:05:52.600
Bye.

00:05:52.659 --> 00:05:53.210
Bye.

00:06:05.880 --> 00:06:06.910
Measurement complete.

00:06:06.910 --> 00:06:09.960
Systolic pressure 158 mmHg.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:11.040
I keep thinking
there's something wrong with this.

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:12.370
The reading is too high.

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:14.860
It's accurate.

00:06:15.650 --> 00:06:16.560
Don't you know

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:18.220
why my blood pressure is high?

00:06:21.750 --> 00:06:22.870
When you're gone,

00:06:22.910 --> 00:06:25.370
my blood pressure
will be perfectly normal.

00:06:25.530 --> 00:06:26.010
Fine.

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:33.230
Take this.

00:06:34.270 --> 00:06:35.330
Congratulations.

00:06:35.640 --> 00:06:36.960
You got what you wanted.

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:40.420
[Notice Regarding the Reassignment
of Comrade Hu Wenjing]

00:06:43.430 --> 00:06:44.230
Director Dai.

00:06:46.780 --> 00:06:48.430
Since I graduated from the police academy,

00:06:48.430 --> 00:06:50.890
you've been
the first person I've followed.

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:53.400
For these 14 or 15 years,

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.950
you've always looked out for me.

00:06:56.350 --> 00:06:57.550
Now that I'm leaving,

00:06:58.190 --> 00:06:59.700
it really feels bittersweet.

00:06:59.700 --> 00:07:01.430
I'm reluctant to part with you.

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:04.240
If you're reluctant, then don't go.

00:07:05.190 --> 00:07:07.600
I don't know what's
so good about the City Bureau.

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:08.600
With your temper,

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:10.850
you'll suffer
a lot of grievances out there.

00:07:10.850 --> 00:07:11.950
Isn't it for the kids?

00:07:11.950 --> 00:07:14.240
If I have to suffer
a bit for them, so be it.

00:07:16.870 --> 00:07:17.390
Just go.

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:19.120
After you leave,

00:07:19.420 --> 00:07:21.350
my ears can finally get some peace.

00:07:21.540 --> 00:07:21.950
No, I...

00:07:21.950 --> 00:07:23.360
I'm not leaving just yet.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:25.160
The Municipal Narcotics Unit said

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:26.240
I should work with Jin Longzheng first

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:28.040
and finish this case before I go.

00:07:30.580 --> 00:07:31.980
Fine, whatever you want.

00:07:32.390 --> 00:07:33.920
About my transfer,

00:07:33.920 --> 00:07:34.970
don't announce it just yet.

00:07:34.970 --> 00:07:35.920
As for Zhang Yan and the others,

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:38.250
I'll tell them privately when I have time.

00:07:39.430 --> 00:07:40.159
Take a break.

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:48.560
By the way,

00:07:49.040 --> 00:07:50.450
in the next couple of days,

00:07:50.450 --> 00:07:52.100
tell your dad and the two kids

00:07:52.480 --> 00:07:53.810
to come over for dinner.

00:07:54.909 --> 00:07:55.520
Okay.

00:07:56.080 --> 00:07:56.560
Okay.

00:07:57.430 --> 00:07:58.480
Stop measuring
your blood pressure all the time.

00:07:58.480 --> 00:07:59.800
It's fine.

00:08:09.620 --> 00:08:10.660
Is it almost done?

00:08:26.890 --> 00:08:27.690
Is it done?

00:08:27.990 --> 00:08:28.990
Perfect timing.

00:08:29.830 --> 00:08:30.430
It's done.

00:08:31.060 --> 00:08:32.049
Let's grab lunch later.

00:08:32.049 --> 00:08:32.659
Okay.

00:08:36.370 --> 00:08:36.960
Ms. Du,

00:08:37.870 --> 00:08:40.130
I've been waiting for almost 10 minutes.

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:52.280
Is Wang Ping really on drugs?

00:08:52.460 --> 00:08:54.150
Of course it's true.

00:08:54.470 --> 00:08:55.150
Didn't she go to

00:08:55.150 --> 00:08:57.320
that rehab center every day before?

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:59.930
Everyone in our department knows.

00:09:00.260 --> 00:09:00.910
They say

00:09:00.910 --> 00:09:02.240
her whole family uses.

00:09:03.090 --> 00:09:04.690
Her whole family uses drugs?

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:05.810
You can't tell.

00:09:05.830 --> 00:09:06.960
She seems so honest.

00:09:07.030 --> 00:09:07.630
Honest?

00:09:07.630 --> 00:09:08.960
She's not honest at all.

00:09:09.390 --> 00:09:09.910
Think about it.

00:09:09.910 --> 00:09:12.370
She takes drugs
but still keeps her job here.

00:09:12.750 --> 00:09:15.080
She must be involved with the leadership.

00:09:15.300 --> 00:09:16.540
Just think.

00:09:17.400 --> 00:09:19.300
She hasn't had a boyfriend
in over 30 years.

00:09:19.300 --> 00:09:20.060
Right?

00:09:20.960 --> 00:09:21.720
Oh my god.

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:22.720
Think about it.

00:09:28.840 --> 00:09:29.390
Come in.

00:09:30.130 --> 00:09:30.770
Mr. Sun.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:32.850
What is it?

00:09:35.110 --> 00:09:36.310
Don't close the door.

00:09:38.680 --> 00:09:40.370
It's about the drug use again.

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:43.080
Everyone outside is

00:09:43.560 --> 00:09:44.680
talking about it.

00:09:44.910 --> 00:09:46.200
You know,

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:47.550
I took it by mistake.

00:09:47.580 --> 00:09:48.030
Right?

00:09:48.150 --> 00:09:49.440
And because of this,

00:09:49.740 --> 00:09:51.540
I helped the police solve a case.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:54.800
Could you please
explain it to everyone for me?

00:09:55.790 --> 00:09:56.700
Look,

00:09:57.200 --> 00:09:58.320
the factory

00:09:58.350 --> 00:10:00.670
has already communicated with the police.

00:10:00.670 --> 00:10:02.030
You weren't fired,

00:10:02.030 --> 00:10:03.890
which is the best clarification.

00:10:04.150 --> 00:10:06.210
Is that all you wanted to see me about?

00:10:07.150 --> 00:10:09.150
But everyone else doesn't think so.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:10.360
They say

00:10:10.750 --> 00:10:12.470
the reason I wasn't fired

00:10:12.510 --> 00:10:15.110
is because of
my connections with the leaders.

00:10:18.790 --> 00:10:19.870
When I was young,

00:10:19.930 --> 00:10:20.650
you see,

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:22.270
I actually wanted

00:10:22.270 --> 00:10:23.720
to have connections with leaders

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:25.450
so I could scare my colleagues.

00:10:25.670 --> 00:10:27.130
But I never had the chance.

00:10:27.500 --> 00:10:28.190
Well,

00:10:28.410 --> 00:10:29.250
Mr. Sun,

00:10:29.280 --> 00:10:31.280
please help me explain to everyone.

00:10:31.620 --> 00:10:33.950
Otherwise, I feel really uncomfortable.

00:10:34.510 --> 00:10:35.320
I know about

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.290
your situation.

00:10:36.900 --> 00:10:38.240
But you can see I'm busy,

00:10:38.260 --> 00:10:38.660
right?

00:10:39.150 --> 00:10:40.360
How about this?

00:10:40.480 --> 00:10:42.000
Go back to work for now.

00:10:42.300 --> 00:10:43.270
Don't think about all that useless stuff.

00:10:43.270 --> 00:10:44.120
Doing a good job

00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:45.550
is better than anything else.

00:10:45.550 --> 00:10:46.070
Go on.

00:11:13.480 --> 00:11:13.940
Mr. Sun.

00:11:14.100 --> 00:11:14.820
Come in.

00:11:23.590 --> 00:11:25.820
The room turned out pretty clean
after it was tidied up.

00:11:25.820 --> 00:11:26.640
So, what do you say?

00:11:26.640 --> 00:11:27.810
Who gets this room?

00:11:28.200 --> 00:11:29.240
Me, of course.

00:11:29.550 --> 00:11:30.600
Just treat me

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:32.080
as your superior for now.

00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:35.400
You just promoted yourself unilaterally.

00:11:36.150 --> 00:11:37.030
The view upstairs

00:11:37.030 --> 00:11:37.870
is actually better.

00:11:37.870 --> 00:11:38.550
You just

00:11:39.280 --> 00:11:40.340
go upstairs later.

00:11:41.790 --> 00:11:42.200
Give it to me.

00:11:42.200 --> 00:11:42.550
Give it to me.

00:11:42.550 --> 00:11:43.510
You're limping.

00:11:43.910 --> 00:11:45.370
What did you tell your dad?

00:11:46.690 --> 00:11:49.240
I didn't dare tell him
I joined the Narcotics Brigade.

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:51.770
I told him I was going
to the Archives Section.

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:53.150
Won't your dad have a breakdown

00:11:53.150 --> 00:11:54.240
when he finds out?

00:11:54.670 --> 00:11:55.030
I'll deal with it

00:11:55.030 --> 00:11:56.720
when he finds out.

00:11:57.550 --> 00:11:59.270
Hurry up and take the suitcase upstairs.

00:11:59.270 --> 00:12:00.330
Time to get to work.

00:12:00.790 --> 00:12:01.310
Right.

00:12:01.520 --> 00:12:02.640
You're zoning out.

00:12:14.270 --> 00:12:14.510
Here.

00:12:14.510 --> 00:12:15.040
This one.

00:12:15.390 --> 00:12:17.230
This is where the motorcycle was stolen.

00:12:17.230 --> 00:12:17.680
Here?

00:12:17.710 --> 00:12:18.260
Right.

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:21.830
Then where did Ding Lai
pick up the package?

00:12:21.830 --> 00:12:23.000
Not here.

00:12:23.670 --> 00:12:24.870
Where he picked up the package is

00:12:24.870 --> 00:12:25.400
this way.

00:12:31.750 --> 00:12:32.270
Here.

00:12:38.360 --> 00:12:40.220
There's nothing if we turn right.

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:42.960
It's here.

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:44.540
This shelf, right?

00:12:46.150 --> 00:12:46.600
Here?

00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:47.410
Right here.

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:49.440
The courier put the package here,

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:50.630
and Ding Lai took it.

00:12:53.390 --> 00:12:55.750
There's some distance
between these two places.

00:12:55.750 --> 00:12:56.630
So, what's the plan?

00:12:56.630 --> 00:12:57.390
Same as last time?

00:12:57.390 --> 00:12:58.240
Let's investigate?

00:12:58.240 --> 00:12:59.770
How do we investigate this?

00:12:59.950 --> 00:13:01.680
These houses all look the same.

00:13:02.120 --> 00:13:03.270
If we go door to door,

00:13:03.270 --> 00:13:04.870
it'll take forever.

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:07.630
Use your old trick.

00:13:08.220 --> 00:13:10.220
Stomp your feet and call for backup.

00:13:10.450 --> 00:13:11.220
I...

00:13:11.270 --> 00:13:12.510
I'm not very familiar with this area.

00:13:12.510 --> 00:13:13.840
Is there any place
in this town you don't know?

00:13:13.840 --> 00:13:15.200
Nuanhai Town has a population of 140,000.

00:13:15.200 --> 00:13:16.600
I can't know everyone.

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:18.550
But I do have a friend

00:13:18.740 --> 00:13:19.860
who lives nearby.

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:24.840
Speak of the devil.

00:13:25.910 --> 00:13:26.510
Slow down.

00:13:29.840 --> 00:13:30.600
Li Xiaoya.

00:13:32.910 --> 00:13:33.750
Wenjing?

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:34.670
Make yourselves at home.

00:13:34.670 --> 00:13:36.000
I'll get you some water.

00:13:36.390 --> 00:13:37.910
This is just a warehouse.

00:13:37.910 --> 00:13:38.870
You're so busy,

00:13:38.870 --> 00:13:40.470
and no one's here to help you?

00:13:40.510 --> 00:13:42.710
Xiaodong comes over to help sometimes.

00:13:42.960 --> 00:13:43.870
You two are already...

00:13:43.870 --> 00:13:45.320
Stop calling him over.

00:13:45.670 --> 00:13:47.240
Old habits die hard.

00:13:47.750 --> 00:13:49.150
An ex-husband as free labor,

00:13:49.150 --> 00:13:50.480
isn't that a good thing?

00:13:50.560 --> 00:13:52.040
As long as I don't have

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:53.600
any other men here,

00:13:53.600 --> 00:13:55.000
he's fine with anything.

00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:56.490
Handsome.

00:13:56.600 --> 00:13:57.000
Thanks.

00:13:57.000 --> 00:13:58.150
This is my colleague, Jin Longzheng.

00:13:58.150 --> 00:13:59.270
Just call me Jin.

00:13:59.270 --> 00:13:59.960
Jin.

00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:01.390
Sit.

00:14:01.540 --> 00:14:03.090
I'll take a look around first.

00:14:03.090 --> 00:14:03.570
Sure.

00:14:05.360 --> 00:14:07.280
Can you sell all this stuff?

00:14:07.310 --> 00:14:08.110
I can sell it all.

00:14:08.110 --> 00:14:09.510
Those are best-sellers.

00:14:09.720 --> 00:14:10.780
The room ends here?

00:14:16.600 --> 00:14:17.630
Come, take a look.

00:14:17.630 --> 00:14:18.720
See if you need anything.

00:14:18.720 --> 00:14:19.240
If you want to buy something,

00:14:19.240 --> 00:14:20.030
place an order right now.

00:14:20.030 --> 00:14:20.720
Okay.

00:14:21.160 --> 00:14:22.040
Let me see.

00:14:22.270 --> 00:14:23.270
Whatever you want,

00:14:23.270 --> 00:14:24.150
just tell me.

00:14:26.080 --> 00:14:26.960
Are you guys

00:14:27.410 --> 00:14:28.800
investigating a case around here?

00:14:28.800 --> 00:14:29.680
Is there a case?

00:14:31.190 --> 00:14:33.120
We're always busy with this stuff.

00:14:34.920 --> 00:14:36.320
Let me ask you something.

00:14:38.950 --> 00:14:41.080
Have you seen this person around here?

00:14:48.270 --> 00:14:49.230
This guy...

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:51.600
Why does he look so familiar?

00:14:51.790 --> 00:14:53.990
The one who pulled a gun at Black Forest.

00:14:56.370 --> 00:14:57.830
Right, right. That's him.

00:14:59.740 --> 00:15:01.000
Isn't he a drug dealer?

00:15:02.200 --> 00:15:03.000
Didn't he die?

00:15:03.000 --> 00:15:03.560
That's what I heard.

00:15:03.560 --> 00:15:03.920
Yes.

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:05.440
He was active here before he died.

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:06.630
That's why we're looking here.

00:15:06.630 --> 00:15:08.690
Take a good look. Do you remember him?

00:15:09.030 --> 00:15:09.670
I remember.

00:15:09.670 --> 00:15:11.200
I only saw him that one time.

00:15:12.790 --> 00:15:14.000
You haven't seen him again

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:15.390
around here, right?

00:15:15.390 --> 00:15:16.230
No.

00:15:16.820 --> 00:15:18.310
He was active around here?

00:15:19.320 --> 00:15:20.550
Did he have accomplices?

00:15:20.550 --> 00:15:21.240
Then I'm in serious danger

00:15:21.240 --> 00:15:21.870
staying here.

00:15:21.870 --> 00:15:22.870
We're looking into that right now.

00:15:22.870 --> 00:15:24.400
Checking for accomplices.

00:15:25.360 --> 00:15:26.000
Show her that.

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:27.060
Take a look at this.

00:15:27.080 --> 00:15:29.410
Does this person's outfit look familiar?

00:15:31.870 --> 00:15:33.000
How can I see anything?

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:34.000
It's all pixelated.

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:34.360
You...

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:37.220
-Get her a clearer one.
-Let me show you another one.

00:15:38.500 --> 00:15:39.150
Here.

00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:40.410
Look at this one.

00:15:50.240 --> 00:15:50.550
No.

00:15:50.720 --> 00:15:51.200
No.

00:15:51.720 --> 00:15:52.650
I don't know him.

00:15:53.370 --> 00:15:54.880
Are these all his accomplices?

00:15:54.880 --> 00:15:55.720
We don't know yet.

00:15:55.720 --> 00:15:57.650
We have to investigate to find out.

00:15:57.750 --> 00:15:59.630
Since you moved here,

00:15:59.720 --> 00:16:01.910
do you know any of your neighbors

00:16:01.930 --> 00:16:03.460
or anyone in the community?

00:16:04.080 --> 00:16:05.240
No, I don't.

00:16:05.260 --> 00:16:06.390
I don't know anyone.

00:16:06.670 --> 00:16:07.630
I just send out deliveries every day.

00:16:07.630 --> 00:16:08.480
I don't go out.

00:16:09.060 --> 00:16:09.950
Great, a wasted trip.

00:16:09.950 --> 00:16:11.210
How is it a wasted trip?

00:16:11.230 --> 00:16:12.600
I'll get you something good.

00:16:12.600 --> 00:16:13.120
No, don't.

00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:13.870
Don't bother.

00:16:13.870 --> 00:16:15.150
This is my new sunscreen.

00:16:15.150 --> 00:16:15.750
Take it.

00:16:16.070 --> 00:16:16.790
You need sun protection.

00:16:16.790 --> 00:16:18.120
The last one didn't work.

00:16:18.120 --> 00:16:18.910
My skin got ruined.

00:16:18.910 --> 00:16:19.840
This is a new version.

00:16:19.840 --> 00:16:20.630
It'll definitely protect you.

00:16:20.630 --> 00:16:21.390
Trust me.

00:16:21.390 --> 00:16:21.790
Trust me.

00:16:21.790 --> 00:16:23.270
You don't have anything good.

00:16:23.270 --> 00:16:24.200
Long, right?

00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:24.720
Jin.

00:16:25.150 --> 00:16:26.030
Here, for you.

00:16:26.030 --> 00:16:26.830
I really don't need it.

00:16:26.830 --> 00:16:27.890
I have no use for it.

00:16:28.000 --> 00:16:28.840
I don't use this stuff.

00:16:28.840 --> 00:16:29.550
Give it to your girlfriend.

00:16:29.550 --> 00:16:30.080
No, no.

00:16:30.320 --> 00:16:31.240
Then I really don't need it.

00:16:31.240 --> 00:16:32.240
I really can't use this.

00:16:32.240 --> 00:16:33.360
I haven't even finished the last one.

00:16:33.360 --> 00:16:34.270
I'll get you another one.

00:16:34.270 --> 00:16:34.600
No need.

00:16:34.600 --> 00:16:35.240
One is enough.

00:16:35.240 --> 00:16:35.670
I have even better ones.

00:16:35.670 --> 00:16:36.630
I'll take this.

00:16:36.660 --> 00:16:37.600
I don't really need it.

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:39.120
This is from a new agent

00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:40.480
I signed in Hainan.

00:16:40.550 --> 00:16:41.550
This is

00:16:41.910 --> 00:16:42.840
top-tier stuff.

00:16:44.270 --> 00:16:45.030
It's really good.

00:16:45.030 --> 00:16:45.600
Fine, one pack is enough.

00:16:45.600 --> 00:16:46.390
I guarantee you'll like it.

00:16:46.390 --> 00:16:47.390
One pack is enough.

00:16:47.390 --> 00:16:47.910
Tell me when you finish it.

00:16:47.910 --> 00:16:48.800
I'll get you more.

00:16:48.800 --> 00:16:50.530
I'm counting on this to be a hit.

00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:52.200
I'm going to be rich.

00:16:52.200 --> 00:16:53.130
I'm telling you.

00:16:54.700 --> 00:16:55.390
Try it later.

00:16:55.390 --> 00:16:56.440
Okay, wait for me.

00:16:56.440 --> 00:16:57.770
We're heading over now.

00:16:58.590 --> 00:16:59.590
Time to go, right?

00:16:59.630 --> 00:17:00.120
Something came up.

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:01.480
This makes it look like
I came just to take this.

00:17:01.480 --> 00:17:02.150
It's fine. Take it.

00:17:02.150 --> 00:17:03.810
Like I came for free products.

00:17:04.200 --> 00:17:05.880
Let me get you some water.

00:17:05.880 --> 00:17:06.270
No need.

00:17:06.270 --> 00:17:06.750
I have some in the car.

00:17:06.750 --> 00:17:08.069
Take a bottle of water for the road.

00:17:08.069 --> 00:17:09.160
There's water in the car.

00:17:09.160 --> 00:17:09.720
Listen to me.

00:17:09.720 --> 00:17:11.160
Remember the photo I just showed you.

00:17:11.160 --> 00:17:12.829
Keep a clear image in your mind.

00:17:12.829 --> 00:17:14.960
If you notice anything wrong around you,

00:17:14.960 --> 00:17:16.490
call us immediately, okay?

00:17:16.880 --> 00:17:17.400
Okay.

00:17:17.400 --> 00:17:18.069
No problem.

00:17:18.069 --> 00:17:20.270
You have to tell me if anything happens.

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:22.160
I'm scared living here alone.

00:17:22.160 --> 00:17:22.640
I know.

00:17:22.640 --> 00:17:23.589
I'll tell you.

00:17:23.880 --> 00:17:24.200
Okay, thanks.

00:17:24.200 --> 00:17:25.960
Lock your doors when you sleep alone

00:17:25.960 --> 00:17:26.589
at night.

00:17:27.270 --> 00:17:27.829
Eat well.

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:28.750
Drive safe.

00:17:28.750 --> 00:17:29.200
Bye.

00:17:29.230 --> 00:17:30.680
What happened to Jin's leg?

00:17:30.680 --> 00:17:31.200
He, um...

00:17:31.200 --> 00:17:31.480
He...

00:17:31.480 --> 00:17:32.070
It's nothing.

00:17:32.070 --> 00:17:33.330
He has an ingrown nail.

00:17:33.370 --> 00:17:33.970
We're off.

00:17:34.680 --> 00:17:36.330
Let's invite Wang Ping
for dinner sometime.

00:17:36.330 --> 00:17:36.790
Another day.

00:17:36.790 --> 00:17:38.110
I'll come visit you another day.

00:17:38.110 --> 00:17:38.590
Bye.

00:17:38.610 --> 00:17:39.280
Bye.

00:18:10.680 --> 00:18:11.480
What's wrong?

00:18:11.810 --> 00:18:12.810
Come here, quick.

00:18:13.430 --> 00:18:14.890
Okay, I'll be right there.

00:18:17.610 --> 00:18:18.310
[Nuanfeng;
dead at the junk acquisition station]

00:18:18.310 --> 00:18:19.270
One.

00:18:19.830 --> 00:18:20.760
Two.

00:18:21.240 --> 00:18:22.310
Three.

00:18:22.350 --> 00:18:23.340
Four.

00:18:23.490 --> 00:18:25.490
Five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten.

00:18:25.790 --> 00:18:26.790
Ready or not?

00:18:42.910 --> 00:18:47.550
[Balance: 9851.92 yuan]

00:19:11.320 --> 00:19:11.960
Wenjing, shoe covers.

00:19:11.960 --> 00:19:12.760
Okay, thanks.

00:19:16.680 --> 00:19:17.360
Zhang Yan.

00:19:18.970 --> 00:19:19.660
Wenjing?

00:19:19.860 --> 00:19:21.660
Didn't you go to the City Bureau?

00:19:21.840 --> 00:19:23.400
I'll leave after this case.

00:19:23.720 --> 00:19:24.780
Where is the stuff?

00:19:25.360 --> 00:19:26.420
Give me the ledger.

00:19:30.340 --> 00:19:32.250
We found this ledger in the room.

00:19:32.280 --> 00:19:33.720
It contains records of him

00:19:33.720 --> 00:19:35.030
selling fake drugs.

00:19:35.170 --> 00:19:36.370
It's quite detailed.

00:19:36.920 --> 00:19:38.200
That box on the table contains pills

00:19:38.200 --> 00:19:39.790
we found in the room

00:19:39.790 --> 00:19:41.070
that look like drugs.

00:19:42.200 --> 00:19:42.930
And this.

00:19:43.110 --> 00:19:43.590
Liu.

00:19:45.240 --> 00:19:45.930
This.

00:19:46.730 --> 00:19:48.490
This was found in the victim's hand.

00:19:48.490 --> 00:19:51.020
It looks different
from the ones on the table.

00:19:52.830 --> 00:19:54.270
If those are fake,

00:19:54.270 --> 00:19:55.400
this might be real.

00:19:55.400 --> 00:19:56.360
Is that what you mean?

00:19:56.360 --> 00:19:57.440
Is that right, Xie?

00:19:59.990 --> 00:20:01.200
My preliminary judgment is that

00:20:01.200 --> 00:20:04.330
this is very similar
to the raw materials in Quan's shop.

00:20:04.530 --> 00:20:05.530
Who is the victim?

00:20:06.350 --> 00:20:07.310
Li Baocai.

00:20:07.580 --> 00:20:10.310
On the surface,
he owned this recycling station,

00:20:10.370 --> 00:20:12.570
but he was probably selling fake drugs.

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:14.310
The person who called the police
is the old man at the door

00:20:14.310 --> 00:20:15.720
who came to sell scrap.

00:20:16.660 --> 00:20:17.610
What was the cause of death?

00:20:17.610 --> 00:20:18.570
Overdose?

00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:20.240
No.

00:20:21.510 --> 00:20:22.510
He was strangled.

00:20:26.650 --> 00:20:28.280
A scrap collector.

00:20:28.950 --> 00:20:30.030
He has a room,

00:20:30.300 --> 00:20:31.720
but he won't let anyone in.

00:20:31.720 --> 00:20:32.950
Whenever we come over,

00:20:32.950 --> 00:20:34.460
his door is always locked.

00:20:34.920 --> 00:20:36.650
One time, I really needed the toilet.

00:20:36.650 --> 00:20:37.770
I was bursting.

00:20:38.930 --> 00:20:40.890
My face turned purple.

00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:42.880
So I went to knock on his door.

00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:44.110
No matter how much I knocked,

00:20:44.110 --> 00:20:44.920
he wouldn't open it.

00:20:44.920 --> 00:20:46.920
Sir, is there anything else?

00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:47.960
One time,

00:20:48.310 --> 00:20:50.350
someone came to sell
a junk washing machine.

00:20:50.350 --> 00:20:51.080
He wasn't in,

00:20:51.330 --> 00:20:52.480
so I gave him a call.

00:20:53.200 --> 00:20:53.830
But the phone

00:20:53.830 --> 00:20:55.350
rang inside his room.

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:58.550
Then he hung up on me.

00:20:58.790 --> 00:20:59.750
I went to knock on his door.

00:20:59.750 --> 00:21:00.640
My hand went numb from knocking.

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:01.070
Sir, sir.

00:21:01.070 --> 00:21:01.900
He just wouldn't open it.

00:21:01.900 --> 00:21:02.920
He doesn't like opening the door

00:21:02.920 --> 00:21:03.480
or letting people in.

00:21:03.480 --> 00:21:04.240
Right, right.

00:21:04.240 --> 00:21:05.070
Do you know

00:21:05.090 --> 00:21:06.890
who he usually hangs out with?

00:21:08.640 --> 00:21:11.070
Who he hangs out with...

00:21:12.760 --> 00:21:15.890
There's a guy in the village
named Chuan.

00:21:16.680 --> 00:21:17.160
He

00:21:17.720 --> 00:21:19.820
grew up playing with Baocai.

00:21:20.220 --> 00:21:21.430
What's his full name?

00:21:23.680 --> 00:21:24.550
Jin...

00:21:25.200 --> 00:21:26.170
Cao...

00:21:26.270 --> 00:21:27.030
Jin...

00:21:27.030 --> 00:21:27.640
Chuan.

00:21:27.640 --> 00:21:28.160
Yes.

00:21:28.490 --> 00:21:30.250
His full name is Cao Jinchuan.

00:21:30.400 --> 00:21:31.310
Cao Jinchuan?

00:21:31.330 --> 00:21:32.130
That's right.

00:21:32.660 --> 00:21:33.520
Do you know him?

00:21:34.000 --> 00:21:35.600
That con artist from the bar.

00:21:50.140 --> 00:21:51.340
What brings you here?

00:21:52.750 --> 00:21:54.510
My old house in the countryside

00:21:55.360 --> 00:21:56.470
is empty.

00:21:57.020 --> 00:21:58.750
I don't mind letting you use it,

00:21:59.590 --> 00:22:00.790
but you said that girl

00:22:01.280 --> 00:22:02.680
is mentally challenged.

00:22:03.980 --> 00:22:05.710
She can't take care of herself.

00:22:07.120 --> 00:22:08.380
So I wanted to ask you

00:22:08.400 --> 00:22:10.680
if you could find someone in the village

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:12.720
to take care of her.

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:16.960
Then you'll have to pay.

00:22:17.130 --> 00:22:17.610
Sure.

00:22:18.920 --> 00:22:20.120
Is 800 a month enough?

00:22:21.750 --> 00:22:22.200
Okay.

00:22:23.270 --> 00:22:24.570
I'll ask around for you.

00:22:24.570 --> 00:22:26.430
I'll let you know when I have news.

00:22:28.000 --> 00:22:28.590
Thanks.

00:22:30.550 --> 00:22:31.510
This matter

00:22:31.870 --> 00:22:33.800
has made me very anxious recently.

00:22:34.550 --> 00:22:35.240
Well,

00:22:35.620 --> 00:22:37.690
I have to check my inventory later,

00:22:37.880 --> 00:22:38.720
so I won't see you out.

00:22:38.720 --> 00:22:39.280
Okay.

00:22:39.440 --> 00:22:40.170
I'm leaving.

00:22:45.270 --> 00:22:47.230
Selling things online,

00:22:47.890 --> 00:22:49.350
are there any tricks to it?

00:22:50.790 --> 00:22:52.650
Do you want to open an online shop?

00:22:53.650 --> 00:22:54.400
Like yours,

00:22:54.400 --> 00:22:56.530
posting on WeChat Moments is fine too.

00:22:58.140 --> 00:22:59.800
How many contacts do you have?

00:23:01.350 --> 00:23:02.880
Between one and two hundred.

00:23:02.880 --> 00:23:04.410
Just over a hundred people?

00:23:04.670 --> 00:23:06.400
Do they have purchasing power?

00:23:09.110 --> 00:23:10.440
You have so few contacts,

00:23:10.440 --> 00:23:12.230
and they have no purchasing power.

00:23:12.230 --> 00:23:13.400
You won't succeed.

00:23:14.400 --> 00:23:15.310
I'm doing so well

00:23:15.310 --> 00:23:16.720
because, look,

00:23:16.840 --> 00:23:18.550
the people in my WeChat Moments

00:23:18.550 --> 00:23:19.920
are all contacts I've accumulated

00:23:19.920 --> 00:23:21.070
over the years.

00:23:21.100 --> 00:23:22.360
They are all young girls.

00:23:22.360 --> 00:23:23.840
I sell whatever they like:

00:23:23.950 --> 00:23:25.150
facial masks, bags,

00:23:25.350 --> 00:23:26.680
and skincare products.

00:23:26.680 --> 00:23:29.250
First, you need to know
who your customers are,

00:23:29.250 --> 00:23:30.770
then decide what to sell.

00:23:31.040 --> 00:23:32.900
Have you decided what to sell yet?

00:23:33.510 --> 00:23:34.030
No.

00:23:34.050 --> 00:23:34.720
I haven't thought it through.

00:23:34.720 --> 00:23:36.680
Just had a sudden idea.

00:23:36.790 --> 00:23:37.920
Then you need to know

00:23:37.930 --> 00:23:39.130
what you're selling.

00:23:39.400 --> 00:23:41.110
You also need to understand
the product's features,

00:23:41.110 --> 00:23:42.070
its advantages,

00:23:42.070 --> 00:23:43.120
and figure it all out.

00:23:43.120 --> 00:23:45.580
That's how you know
how to sell to customers.

00:23:47.120 --> 00:23:48.250
I'll think about it.

00:23:49.680 --> 00:23:50.550
If you really can't figure it out,

00:23:50.550 --> 00:23:51.620
bring it over and I'll take a look.

00:23:51.620 --> 00:23:52.650
I'm a professional.

00:23:52.650 --> 00:23:53.080
Okay.

00:23:54.390 --> 00:23:54.790
Bye.

00:23:54.790 --> 00:23:55.850
I won't see you out.

00:23:58.180 --> 00:23:58.820
Xiaodong.

00:23:59.610 --> 00:24:00.130
Ken.

00:24:00.160 --> 00:24:01.040
Why are you here?

00:24:01.040 --> 00:24:01.760
I...

00:24:01.790 --> 00:24:03.190
asked Xiaoya for a favor.

00:24:03.610 --> 00:24:04.610
You're done talking?

00:24:04.610 --> 00:24:05.340
I'm leaving.

00:24:18.120 --> 00:24:19.980
What did my brother want with you?

00:24:21.290 --> 00:24:22.130
Your brother?

00:24:23.820 --> 00:24:24.940
He said

00:24:25.750 --> 00:24:26.940
he wants to find a place to live

00:24:26.940 --> 00:24:27.860
for a girl,

00:24:27.890 --> 00:24:29.690
and she's mentally challenged.

00:24:29.950 --> 00:24:30.840
Your brother

00:24:31.680 --> 00:24:33.360
isn't trafficking women, is he?

00:24:33.360 --> 00:24:33.960
No.

00:24:34.360 --> 00:24:35.760
He doesn't have the guts.

00:24:38.200 --> 00:24:40.330
Why did you call me here in such a hurry?

00:24:40.840 --> 00:24:43.050
[Nuanfeng Hengli Electronics]

00:25:44.450 --> 00:25:45.210
Who are you?

00:25:45.960 --> 00:25:47.360
Why are you following me?

00:25:49.430 --> 00:25:50.490
Don't get me wrong.

00:25:51.390 --> 00:25:52.980
You're Wang Ping, right?

00:25:53.850 --> 00:25:54.520
I know you.

00:25:55.070 --> 00:25:56.440
We work at the same factory.

00:25:56.440 --> 00:25:57.760
I'm in the Outreach Department.

00:25:57.760 --> 00:25:58.410
Han Qiang.

00:26:01.280 --> 00:26:02.520
What do you want?

00:26:05.920 --> 00:26:07.360
I heard

00:26:08.520 --> 00:26:10.520
you've used sugar too, haven't you?

00:26:13.660 --> 00:26:14.770
I'm not finished.

00:26:18.200 --> 00:26:19.330
I've used sugar too.

00:26:21.330 --> 00:26:22.490
But I've quit now,

00:26:23.940 --> 00:26:25.600
and no one knows I ever used it.

00:26:27.890 --> 00:26:29.130
Seeing that

00:26:29.560 --> 00:26:32.490
you're being bullied
by colleagues because of this,

00:26:33.100 --> 00:26:34.500
I really want to help you.

00:26:37.000 --> 00:26:37.960
Thank you,

00:26:38.720 --> 00:26:39.520
but no thanks.

00:26:41.400 --> 00:26:42.830
Can I buy you lunch then?

00:26:43.240 --> 00:26:43.680
No.

00:26:43.680 --> 00:26:45.660
I have to go home and cook for my brother.

00:26:45.660 --> 00:26:47.590
Didn't your brother use sugar too?

00:26:50.790 --> 00:26:51.920
How do you know that?

00:26:53.640 --> 00:26:55.370
I heard it from our colleagues.

00:26:56.110 --> 00:26:57.350
They love

00:26:57.570 --> 00:26:59.570
gossiping about people's privacy.

00:27:00.840 --> 00:27:02.430
But I'd rather believe

00:27:02.920 --> 00:27:05.310
the version where you helped
the police solve the case.

00:27:05.310 --> 00:27:06.440
I think you should

00:27:06.680 --> 00:27:08.280
stand up and respond to them.

00:27:10.510 --> 00:27:11.310
I don't dare.

00:27:12.720 --> 00:27:14.440
Can you let go of my arm?

00:27:15.400 --> 00:27:16.560
I can help you.

00:27:20.160 --> 00:27:21.220
What are you doing?

00:27:21.590 --> 00:27:22.030
Wang An.

00:27:22.030 --> 00:27:23.310
What do you think?

00:27:23.310 --> 00:27:23.790
Wang An!

00:27:24.110 --> 00:27:24.740
What are you doing?

00:27:24.740 --> 00:27:25.400
Let go of me!

00:27:25.590 --> 00:27:26.590
-This is my brother.
-What are you doing?

00:27:26.590 --> 00:27:27.310
What do you think I'm doing?

00:27:27.310 --> 00:27:27.830
Wang An!

00:27:28.200 --> 00:27:28.510
Well,

00:27:28.510 --> 00:27:29.350
this is my brother,

00:27:29.350 --> 00:27:29.720
Wang An.

00:27:29.720 --> 00:27:31.110
Didn't you see he started it?

00:27:31.110 --> 00:27:32.070
What are you doing?

00:27:32.070 --> 00:27:33.200
This is my brother.

00:27:33.220 --> 00:27:34.060
Let go,

00:27:34.480 --> 00:27:35.240
now!

00:27:36.080 --> 00:27:37.080
Wang An, get up.

00:27:37.100 --> 00:27:38.010
Let me see.

00:27:38.460 --> 00:27:39.270
Get up.

00:27:39.960 --> 00:27:41.400
Are you okay? Come on.

00:27:42.610 --> 00:27:43.440
Get up.

00:27:46.720 --> 00:27:47.480
Wang Ping.

00:27:51.870 --> 00:27:53.670
Contact me if you need anything.

00:28:08.290 --> 00:28:09.100
Let me see.

00:28:11.110 --> 00:28:11.870
I'm fine.

00:28:13.150 --> 00:28:13.780
Wang An.

00:28:25.650 --> 00:28:27.910
What's your relationship with that guy?

00:28:30.340 --> 00:28:31.120
He's my colleague.

00:28:31.120 --> 00:28:31.880
Why?

00:28:32.940 --> 00:28:34.550
A colleague holding your hand,

00:28:34.550 --> 00:28:35.550
walking you home?

00:28:37.920 --> 00:28:39.360
If I weren't home,

00:28:40.100 --> 00:28:42.030
would you have brought him inside?

00:28:42.590 --> 00:28:44.650
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:28:45.270 --> 00:28:46.710
I don't even know him.

00:28:48.310 --> 00:28:49.310
You just said he was a colleague,

00:28:49.310 --> 00:28:50.570
now you don't know him?

00:28:52.080 --> 00:28:54.510
There are over 2,000 people
at my workplace.

00:28:54.510 --> 00:28:56.070
I can't know everyone.

00:28:57.240 --> 00:28:58.640
What did he want with you?

00:29:05.250 --> 00:29:06.370
He wanted to do me a favor.

00:29:06.370 --> 00:29:07.170
What favor?

00:29:08.020 --> 00:29:09.950
My work has nothing to do with you.

00:29:09.970 --> 00:29:11.380
Everything about you concerns me.

00:29:11.380 --> 00:29:12.090
Wang An.

00:29:13.490 --> 00:29:14.490
I'm your sister.

00:29:15.310 --> 00:29:16.070
Do I have to report to you

00:29:16.070 --> 00:29:16.920
about everything I do

00:29:16.920 --> 00:29:18.310
and everyone I meet?

00:29:20.160 --> 00:29:21.110
I feed you and take care of you,

00:29:21.110 --> 00:29:23.710
and now you don't even
know your place anymore?

00:29:27.620 --> 00:29:28.920
The deceased is named Li Baocai.

00:29:28.920 --> 00:29:29.880
The body was found

00:29:29.880 --> 00:29:31.920
around 12:15 PM today.

00:29:32.070 --> 00:29:33.640
His neighbor called the police.

00:29:33.640 --> 00:29:34.590
According to forensics,

00:29:34.590 --> 00:29:36.400
the time of death
was the day before yesterday,

00:29:36.400 --> 00:29:37.680
on the afternoon of the 20th,

00:29:37.680 --> 00:29:39.070
between 6:30 and 7:30.

00:29:39.790 --> 00:29:41.440
The cause of death
was manual strangulation,

00:29:41.440 --> 00:29:42.640
causing blocked neck vessels

00:29:42.640 --> 00:29:44.550
and reflex cardiac arrest.

00:29:44.690 --> 00:29:45.400
Before he died,

00:29:45.400 --> 00:29:47.440
he took an overdose of a new drug.

00:29:47.440 --> 00:29:49.200
The composition of this new drug

00:29:49.200 --> 00:29:50.880
matches the undiluted raw materials

00:29:50.880 --> 00:29:52.960
we found in the Quan case.

00:29:52.960 --> 00:29:53.760
We can infer

00:29:53.790 --> 00:29:54.960
that these two drugs

00:29:54.960 --> 00:29:56.220
came from the same lab.

00:29:57.550 --> 00:29:58.160
Cao Jinchuan.

00:29:58.160 --> 00:29:59.200
Male, 35.

00:29:59.200 --> 00:30:01.160
From Wujing Village,
Nuanhai Town, Nuanfeng County.

00:30:01.160 --> 00:30:03.890
He was Li Baocai's partner
in selling fake drugs.

00:30:03.920 --> 00:30:05.310
He is currently the prime suspect.

00:30:05.310 --> 00:30:06.640
He's on the run.

00:30:06.640 --> 00:30:08.790
He bought 3 train tickets
the day before yesterday

00:30:08.790 --> 00:30:11.310
for Wuhan, Xiamen, and Changchun.

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:12.590
This suggests

00:30:12.590 --> 00:30:15.110
he has counter-reconnaissance awareness.

00:30:15.400 --> 00:30:17.270
We're contacting the railway department

00:30:17.270 --> 00:30:19.510
to confirm which train he took.

00:30:44.220 --> 00:30:44.640
What are you doing?

00:30:44.640 --> 00:30:45.440
What are you doing?

00:30:45.440 --> 00:30:46.700
Where did you get this?

00:30:48.400 --> 00:30:49.400
It's not mine.

00:30:49.440 --> 00:30:50.590
I found it in your pants pocket.

00:30:50.590 --> 00:30:51.590
And it's not yours?

00:30:51.590 --> 00:30:52.960
What did you promise me
at the rehab center?

00:30:52.960 --> 00:30:54.440
Didn't you say you'd
never touch this stuff again?

00:30:54.440 --> 00:30:55.310
Tell me!

00:30:57.440 --> 00:30:58.600
How should I know?

00:30:58.940 --> 00:31:00.490
Besides, Tang Sile is dead.

00:31:00.920 --> 00:31:01.960
Even if I wanted to buy some,
there's nowhere to get it.

00:31:01.960 --> 00:31:04.020
So you still want to buy it, don't you?

00:31:05.430 --> 00:31:06.430
No, I don't.

00:31:07.440 --> 00:31:09.170
I really didn't want to buy any.

00:31:16.510 --> 00:31:17.780
Why won't you believe me?

00:31:17.780 --> 00:31:19.020
How can I believe you?

00:31:19.590 --> 00:31:21.200
Tell me, how can I believe you?

00:31:21.200 --> 00:31:23.240
I found this right in your pants.

00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:23.880
Tell me,

00:31:23.880 --> 00:31:25.680
how am I supposed to believe you?

00:31:33.590 --> 00:31:34.070
Wang An.

00:31:34.070 --> 00:31:34.440
Let go of me!

00:31:34.440 --> 00:31:35.790
Stop fighting, you two.

00:31:35.790 --> 00:31:36.480
Wang An.

00:31:36.790 --> 00:31:37.750
What are you doing?

00:31:37.750 --> 00:31:38.960
This is my brother.

00:31:39.160 --> 00:31:41.030
It must be that colleague of yours.

00:31:41.030 --> 00:31:41.960
He must have slipped it into my pocket

00:31:41.960 --> 00:31:42.960
when I wasn't looking.

00:31:42.960 --> 00:31:43.760
It must be him.

00:31:48.100 --> 00:31:48.690
Fine.

00:31:50.470 --> 00:31:51.030
Come on.

00:31:52.140 --> 00:31:54.140
Then destroy it right in front of me.

00:32:21.990 --> 00:32:23.390
No one would have noticed

00:32:24.830 --> 00:32:26.360
when Ding Lai escaped here.

00:32:27.860 --> 00:32:29.390
And he hadn't left this room

00:32:31.270 --> 00:32:32.820
for the entire month.

00:32:34.860 --> 00:32:36.120
We've cleaned up

00:32:36.760 --> 00:32:38.280
all the traces perfectly.

00:32:39.600 --> 00:32:40.260
No issues.

00:32:44.950 --> 00:32:46.410
You run a micro-business.

00:32:47.140 --> 00:32:48.940
Your accounts are messy anyway,

00:32:49.950 --> 00:32:52.280
so making some extra cash is explainable.

00:32:57.880 --> 00:33:00.080
Unless the police are very suspicious,

00:33:00.860 --> 00:33:02.260
and specifically target

00:33:02.480 --> 00:33:04.240
your WeChat transfer records

00:33:04.540 --> 00:33:05.740
and bank statements,

00:33:07.090 --> 00:33:08.090
or check

00:33:08.450 --> 00:33:09.710
your spending records

00:33:10.290 --> 00:33:11.660
for that entire month.

00:33:13.180 --> 00:33:14.640
Like the amount of groceries

00:33:14.640 --> 00:33:15.350
or takeout.

00:33:15.700 --> 00:33:16.740
That might

00:33:17.470 --> 00:33:18.710
cause some problems.

00:33:20.830 --> 00:33:23.090
But do you think
they'll check that closely?

00:33:23.090 --> 00:33:24.490
If Hu Wenjing finds out

00:33:25.340 --> 00:33:26.380
that for one meal,

00:33:27.270 --> 00:33:28.470
I bought two burgers,

00:33:28.830 --> 00:33:29.720
two orders of fries,

00:33:29.720 --> 00:33:31.520
and six pieces of fried chicken,

00:33:31.750 --> 00:33:32.950
how do I explain that?

00:33:37.880 --> 00:33:39.340
If it really comes to that,

00:33:40.950 --> 00:33:42.950
just say what I told you before.

00:33:44.480 --> 00:33:46.440
We never really lost touch.

00:33:46.920 --> 00:33:48.650
You still have feelings for me,

00:33:48.660 --> 00:33:50.320
and I stay here occasionally.

00:33:50.710 --> 00:33:52.710
When we argued at the intersection,

00:33:53.550 --> 00:33:54.750
just tell Hu Wenjing

00:33:55.180 --> 00:33:57.310
that we were having another conflict.

00:33:57.420 --> 00:33:58.480
Do you understand?

00:34:03.720 --> 00:34:04.980
What about that truck?

00:34:05.100 --> 00:34:06.300
How did you handle it?

00:34:08.590 --> 00:34:09.360
That truck

00:34:09.360 --> 00:34:11.290
belonged to a client in transport.

00:34:11.590 --> 00:34:13.250
He left it with me for repairs.

00:34:13.429 --> 00:34:15.159
I cleaned it up that very night.

00:34:15.659 --> 00:34:17.520
I put the original plates back on,

00:34:17.820 --> 00:34:19.710
and gave it back to him the next day.

00:34:19.710 --> 00:34:20.920
He's not a local.

00:34:21.480 --> 00:34:23.139
He drives all over the country

00:34:23.429 --> 00:34:25.230
and isn't even in this province.

00:34:25.929 --> 00:34:26.560
It's fine.

00:34:27.920 --> 00:34:30.489
Besides, the road Ding Lai
chose is very remote.

00:34:30.489 --> 00:34:32.489
I told you to take the small path back

00:34:32.560 --> 00:34:34.760
to avoid all the intersection cameras.

00:34:36.409 --> 00:34:37.139
Don't worry.

00:34:37.469 --> 00:34:39.150
I cleaned your car up too.

00:34:41.920 --> 00:34:43.179
With me shielding you,

00:34:44.480 --> 00:34:46.030
Ding Lai's death

00:34:46.190 --> 00:34:47.449
won't be traced to you.

00:35:15.800 --> 00:35:16.930
You're so good to me.

00:35:20.020 --> 00:35:21.150
Why didn't I realize

00:35:22.920 --> 00:35:24.400
how good you were before?

00:35:27.190 --> 00:35:29.120
It's not too late to realize it now.

00:35:32.590 --> 00:35:33.400
Then,

00:35:35.190 --> 00:35:36.670
can you move in with me?

00:35:37.910 --> 00:35:39.500
If Hu Wenjing sees

00:35:40.030 --> 00:35:41.690
we're living together again,

00:35:43.130 --> 00:35:44.330
she won't suspect me.

00:35:48.060 --> 00:35:48.870
Good idea.

00:35:52.350 --> 00:35:53.280
I totally agree.

00:36:37.710 --> 00:36:38.640
I shouldn't have

00:36:38.920 --> 00:36:40.520
doubted you so much today.

00:36:41.450 --> 00:36:42.530
I apologize.

00:36:43.110 --> 00:36:44.110
I'm sorry.

00:36:44.440 --> 00:36:45.040
Okay?

00:36:52.410 --> 00:36:54.200
We worked so hard to quit.

00:36:55.440 --> 00:36:57.100
I'm worried about relapsing.

00:36:57.280 --> 00:36:59.680
Didn't the counselor at rehab say

00:37:00.120 --> 00:37:00.850
that drugs

00:37:00.880 --> 00:37:03.670
subtly change our perception,

00:37:03.690 --> 00:37:05.880
making us think they're good?

00:37:20.960 --> 00:37:23.090
I'm not taking the postgraduate exam.

00:37:24.070 --> 00:37:24.590
What?

00:37:26.740 --> 00:37:27.740
I'm not taking the grad school exam.

00:37:27.740 --> 00:37:28.640
Why?

00:37:29.320 --> 00:37:30.400
We've been preparing for 3 years.

00:37:30.400 --> 00:37:31.410
Why stop now?

00:37:31.440 --> 00:37:33.040
It's not that I don't want to.

00:37:33.110 --> 00:37:34.130
It's that I can't.

00:37:34.960 --> 00:37:35.800
Which school

00:37:35.800 --> 00:37:37.310
would accept a student
with a drug history?

00:37:37.310 --> 00:37:37.830
Well.

00:37:37.850 --> 00:37:40.720
Didn't the rehab counselors say
it wouldn't affect that?

00:37:40.720 --> 00:37:42.050
That was to comfort you.

00:37:43.150 --> 00:37:44.280
And you believed it?

00:37:45.840 --> 00:37:46.900
The law also states

00:37:47.440 --> 00:37:49.840
that former drug users shouldn't face
discrimination when job hunting.

00:37:49.840 --> 00:37:52.100
But how many bosses actually don't mind?

00:37:54.430 --> 00:37:56.890
But I'm working at my job
just fine, aren't I?

00:38:06.070 --> 00:38:08.130
Why didn't you call the police today?

00:38:12.830 --> 00:38:14.430
I really was...

00:38:16.210 --> 00:38:17.650
I was impulsive today.

00:38:19.280 --> 00:38:21.510
Now we don't have any evidence left.

00:38:21.940 --> 00:38:24.400
Calling the police
would be useless, wouldn't it?

00:38:24.400 --> 00:38:25.500
Go tell Hu Wenjing.

00:38:26.440 --> 00:38:28.300
She will definitely believe you.

00:38:28.920 --> 00:38:29.550
Enough.

00:38:32.060 --> 00:38:33.800
Better to avoid trouble.

00:38:34.840 --> 00:38:37.060
We can't afford
to offend people like that.

00:38:37.060 --> 00:38:38.520
What if they try to harm us?

00:38:38.590 --> 00:38:39.270
Wang Ping.

00:38:43.300 --> 00:38:45.700
You say you're always afraid I'll relapse.

00:38:46.630 --> 00:38:47.920
But I feel like you're afraid you will...

00:38:47.920 --> 00:38:49.180
Enough, stop talking.

00:38:52.380 --> 00:38:53.640
This matter ends here.

00:38:55.330 --> 00:38:56.930
No one is to mention it again.

00:40:19.040 --> 00:40:27.680
[Next Episode Preview]